{"tid":1684040,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"沖繩世界文化遺產首里城凌晨起火　500年歷史建築物完全燒毀","createTime":"2019-10-31T02:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T03:48:09.000Z","uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5523b519a87494db1f703df825943646d3458219","tid":1684040,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2485000/2486927/okinawa_thumb_20191031_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2485000%2F2486927%2Fokinawa_thumb_20191031_S_600.jpg&h=ac55ba66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本沖繩知名古城兼世界文化遺產「首里城」有500年歷史，但今日凌晨時分發生的一場大火，完全燒毀了首里城的正殿、南北殿、書院、鎖之間、黃金御殿、二階殿等六棟建築物。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>正殿等六棟建築物被燒毀</strong><br />\n<br />\n綜合當地傳媒報導，那霸市消防單位於當地時間凌晨2時41分（香港時間1點41分）接到報告，指首里城發生火災，超過15輛消車趕到現場救災，但整座首里城已經陷入火海，部分主要結構倒塌，並沒有傷亡報告。<br />\n<br />\n沖繩那霸市消防局今早發布的最新消息指出，火災完全燒毀了首里城的正殿、南北殿、書院、鎖之間、黃金御殿、二階殿等六棟建築物，有圍觀民眾指燒到只剩骨架，燒毀面積共4200平方公尺。在火災發生約6個小時後，火勢漸漸平息，但正殿西側的奉神門仍在燃燒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2485000/2486927/5_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2485000%2F2486927%2F5_600.png&h=64147713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據最先抵達的消防員轉述，起火點在正殿附近，然後蔓延至整個建築群，但起火原因暫時未知。據報首里城周日開始舉行「首里城祭」，昨晚與活動相關的籌備工作直至凌晨1時才結束，未知與大火是否有關係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2485000/2486927/6_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2485000%2F2486927%2F6_600.png&h=138aa5e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>專家心痛首里城內文物</strong><br />\n<br />\n首里城是在琉球至國時代，即約500年前建造，為15世紀至19世紀琉球國的都城所在地及王宮。1933年被列為日本國寶，但在二戰期間被美軍砲擊焚毀。1992年展開主體建築復原工作，直至2000年被列為世界文化遺產，1年有超過250萬以上的遊客造訪，是沖繩重要的觀光勝地。<br />\n<br />\n沖繩考古學會顧問當真嗣一表示，特別擔心首里城內保存的寶物、美術品等文化遺產，強調這些文化遺產是琉球文化的核心，並不是金錢的問題。"},{"pid":"2fc50698562958f3808a34891365254b1f672396","tid":1684040,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b95f0d3342cfd202823d10102000d56503f9de","tid":1684040,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecbebf767f7b5ce61cfa5f1b32812fb2b6ef117","tid":1684040,"uid":47020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"去過一次 風景真係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31317487d782b47f4f07c139c8043b5ad9eb94c","tid":1684040,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3Mr418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3Mr418.jpg&h=cefe1d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLpUutT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLpUutT.jpg&h=f08cf9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMJBHOX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMJBHOX.jpg&h=868a8b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGzYbHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGzYbHo.jpg&h=963d3c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8G5c0AP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8G5c0AP.jpg&h=bc4fae3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7eaa396fc681dea81ddac728796c00199675e5e","tid":1684040,"uid":19518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"上年去時仲維修緊，諗住有機會會再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751c4e5691cc124f0c7d159de03b3f3450e91a37","tid":1684040,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7eaa396fc681dea81ddac728796c00199675e5e","tid":1684040,"uid":19518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"上年去時仲維修緊，諗住有機會會再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:13:38.000Z","msg":"Plan左依一兩年去沖繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心痛咁靚既遺跡一晚冇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1239e2184b51dccd1e4556583aff76327405a7d8","tid":1684040,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"屌，裝修佬食煙引起？"}]}